  <brief_title>Caregiver Support in the Coping of Patients Who Are Undergoing a Donor Bone Marrow Transplant</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adjustment to Illness by Survival Rates in Allogeneic Bone Marrow Transplant (BMT): The Relative Importance of Lay Care-Partner Support</official_title>
